<br>
As for our own story... <br>
I am rethinking the whole Book One and Two idea.  After all, this whole section is called &quot;Tales of the Fellowship&quot; and hopefullly some others will continue to tell our story through their own tales.<br>
<br>
There still are a few loose ends to wrap up though, so I will add another chapter or two when time permits.  Since this tale turned out to be a story of how we formed as opposed to our whole history, I am thinking of re-titling the whole thing though!  Perhaps taking the name from one of the chapters...<br>
<br>
&quot;The Eye of the Storm:<br>
The Defintive Tale of the Creation of the Exodus Fellowship!&quot;<br>
<br>
Wow, how's that for long winded?!  I don't think all of that will fit in the thread subject line!<br>
<br>
Other title suggestions are welcome!  <br>
