<br>
I was just a baby toon, maybe 11 - trying to look after me bairns, though they were already too tough for me to help!  Baby enough that a cute little thing called Khaba with an axe as big as he was could impress me!  Lol!  First time I had fought in an arena, but not me first death!  Or (unfortunately) the last...  I think I was 30 before I ever had a rez - just pick up the pieces and move on.<br>
<br>
